
D&D Kids Resources Server (Flask)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
Server running at: http://localhost:8000
Database: F:\DND\Kids Resources\dnd_kids_resources.db
API endpoints:
   - GET /api/spells         (all spells)
   - GET /api/spells/<title> (single spell)
   - GET /api/actions        (all actions)
   - GET /api/actions/<title> (single action)

 Press Ctrl+C to stop the server
